column5: Don't have too muc htime to write a report.  Gotta work at 5am... pics and video will explain it all.
Great report, enjoyed that video ya had there.
nice fish, nice report, and thanks for the video !!!

Great report and cool video. I now this may come across as a stupid question but hear me out. Did you shoot the video with your camera or camcorder? The reason I ask is that I can shoot short video with my camera. Thanks!
Awesome pics and video.............now I can't wait until the weekend!
Those are some nice fish, can't watch the video though...dang dial up  Maureen
Very cool report!  Love the pics and educational video!!
Thanks for the prefish tour Steve.LOL  Nice job on the vid.
Even with limited time, you produced an excellent report, Steve. Great pics too! Thanks for sharing.
Great stuff Steve.  Excellent video - loved the educational aspect to it.
Dang! Its says photobucket site maintenence!!!!!!

haha misfish, I get possession of the new house this weekend so I wont be fishing it, id love to but i cant afford it, and im kinda commited to something else, but they are on deep weeds.  Shot it as about my 67th 1 minute video of the day on my camera, hit delete many times until i got bit on camera haha.
Great report there bro.  Thanks for sharing. Good luck on the house.  John
I thought for sure I posted on this last night....weird.  Anyhow..nice fishies
I could have sworn I editted my post also. Excellant Video! I really enjoyed it! I will try to get some jig and pig fish this weekend!
